injectables.name: CustomDateAdapter

jsdoctags.comment: the current date as date from PC ignoring the "useUtc" configuration

components.name: ButtonFilledComponent
ButtonOutlinedComponent
ButtonTextComponent
DatePickerComponent
components.templateData:
<mat-form-field appearance="fill">
  <mat-label>{{ label }}</mat-label>
  <input matInput formDatePicker readonly [matDatepicker]="dueDatePicker" />
  <mat-datepicker-toggle matSuffix [for]="dueDatePicker">
    <mat-icon matDatepickerToggleIcon class="material-icons-outlined"
      >calendar_today</mat-icon
    >
  </mat-datepicker-toggle>
  <mat-datepicker #dueDatePicker></mat-datepicker>
</mat-form-field>

variables.name: Template
variables.defaultValue:
(
  args: ButtonFilledComponent
) => ({
  props: args,
  template: `
  <alvys-button-filled [disabled]="disabled" [size]="size" (onClick)="onClick($event)" >
    Button
    <mat-icon>keyboard_arrow_down</mat-icon>
  </alvys-button-filled>
  `,
})
